{"tid":2435290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"66歲林青霞自爆已打首針科興疫苗：心情愉快","createTime":"2021-03-06T06:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T08:58:03.000Z","uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78f0184d0069f7a71f823fca3343c93b058c22a0","tid":2435290,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PV-3ouVF-jxKb3vlfnVQfWUDkjA=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SZETVP7LEZB6HI3LCZNUQYQHVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPV-3ouVF-jxKb3vlfnVQfWUDkjA%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSZETVP7LEZB6HI3LCZNUQYQHVU.jpg&h=f455500b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府日前開始安排巿民接種內地的科興疫苗，雖然日前一名有長期病患的63歲男子接種後兩日死亡，但無阻66歲林青霞打針的決心，她昨日凌晨在微博發帖文透露已打了第一劑科興疫苗：「星期三打了第一針科興疫苗感覺很好，沒甚麼反應，心情愉快。」<br />\n<br />\n北京限制只准18至59歲人士接種科興疫苗，以林青霞的年齡其實是超出限制，有fans揶揄偶像：「如果兩針打完，我估計副作用會更明顯，嗯，副作用就是愛炫耀。」除林青霞「超齡」打針外，現年67歲及68歲的肥媽Maria Cordero及陳友，前日也分別在社交網分享「超齡」接種疫苗的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zxdd1VTigOTs0guTJDC8eF8OoD8=/640x550/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CAGDBPVEMRDRBOEOKMWB6OJDLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZxdd1VTigOTs0guTJDC8eF8OoD8%3D%2F640x550%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCAGDBPVEMRDRBOEOKMWB6OJDLE.jpg&h=2589f685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08557c30a284f4763daf997ac0f86ce51fbc5c30","tid":2435290,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210306/UKPDUMXWQZBRBGHGTY7F23HHVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210306%2FUKPDUMXWQ